1
00:00:07,019 --> 00:00:11,220
♪I've braved the storms, walked through the rain♪

2
00:00:11,259 --> 00:00:14,619
♪Seen the highs and lows along the way♪

3
00:00:14,820 --> 00:00:18,019
♪But you stay quiet, never change♪

4
00:00:18,219 --> 00:00:21,620
♪Like a child who dreams beneath the stars♪

5
00:00:21,699 --> 00:00:25,019
♪I've read the story in your eyes♪

6
00:00:25,260 --> 00:00:28,539
♪And finally, nothing's left to hide♪

7
00:00:28,699 --> 00:00:32,140
♪You won't give in to a world so cold♪

8
00:00:32,259 --> 00:00:35,740
♪So you wander through it on your own♪

9
00:00:35,859 --> 00:00:39,340
♪Maybe fate has drawn us near♪

10
00:00:39,420 --> 00:00:42,340
♪Just to help you learn to believe♪

11
00:00:42,579 --> 00:00:45,500
♪Everything you've questioned deep inside♪

12
00:00:45,619 --> 00:00:49,740
♪I'll be the proof you need♪

13
00:00:49,859 --> 00:00:51,179
♪I've made my choice♪

14
00:00:51,259 --> 00:00:54,140
♪For you, I'll be brave and break the rules♪

15
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:57,380
♪What's there to fear even if the world is right and I am wrong?♪

16
00:00:58,060 --> 00:01:00,939
♪One day, all of this will turn into memories♪

17
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:04,379
♪Every storm we faced will turn into our life's scenery♪

18
00:01:05,140 --> 00:01:08,019
♪For you, I'll be brave and break the rules♪

19
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:11,260
♪What's there to fear even if the world is right and I am wrong?♪

20
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:14,819
♪Even if, in the end, the whole world turns against me♪

21
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:18,260
♪I won't regret having loved you♪

22
00:01:18,379 --> 00:01:21,939
♪With all my heart♪

23
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:25,780
♪I've held you close♪

24
00:01:25,859 --> 00:01:29,459
♪Walked by your side♪

25
00:01:29,620 --> 00:01:33,939
♪And loved the fire that burned inside you♪

26
00:01:33,939 --> 00:01:35,480
[The First Frost]

27
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,980
[Adapted from the novel of the same name by Zhu Yi on www.jjwxc.net]

28
00:01:44,870 --> 00:01:45,560
Hello.

29
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,560
Hello.

30
00:01:47,510 --> 00:01:48,790
I'd like to book a room.

31
00:01:50,709 --> 00:01:51,349
Thank you.

32
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,840
All guests must register.

33
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:54,150
I'm not staying.

34
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:56,150
There's one more room next door. Want it?

35
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,280
I'm not staying.

36
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,590
I'm just walking her up.

37
00:01:58,590 --> 00:02:00,120
This is just the usual trick

38
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,150
of you young guys these days.

39
00:02:01,150 --> 00:02:02,120
Rules state

40
00:02:02,349 --> 00:02:03,150
you must register.

41
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:06,150
I can go up myself.

42
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,840
Then remember to lock your door tonight.

43
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,469
Are you still practicing tonight?

44
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,560
I'll probably go over a few moves.

45
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,629
Don't stress. You got this.

46
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,280
You're not the examiner.

47
00:02:19,289 --> 00:02:20,000
How do you know?

48
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:22,750
I know a bit about the arts.

49
00:02:22,870 --> 00:02:24,400
- I think your dancing is... - Hello.

50
00:02:24,909 --> 00:02:25,469
Room 306.

51
00:02:25,909 --> 00:02:26,560
Thank you.

52
00:02:28,189 --> 00:02:28,909
I'm going up now.

53
00:02:31,189 --> 00:02:31,840
Thanks.

54
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,430
Are you sure you don't want the room?

55
00:02:38,629 --> 00:02:39,280
No need.

56
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:39,870
Thanks.

57
00:02:46,750 --> 00:02:47,430
Where are you going?

58
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:49,469
To get a room.

59
00:02:50,189 --> 00:02:51,120
We're fully booked.

60
00:02:52,469 --> 00:02:53,400
Who are you?

61
00:02:54,189 --> 00:02:54,919
Front desk staff.

62
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:57,240
I'll pay extra.

63
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,750
Even with extra, we're still full.

64
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,750
See? The lights are off.

65
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:05,120
Sorry.

66
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:07,240
Try checking ahead.

67
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:33,060
[To Wen Shuangjiang: Just picture the examiners as pumpkins.]

68
00:03:56,189 --> 00:03:57,800
Next up, scene performance.

69
00:03:58,590 --> 00:04:00,189
Candidate No. 7, Wen Yifan,

70
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:01,080
please get ready.

71
00:04:03,219 --> 00:04:06,699
♪My heart races, and even my breath pauses♪

72
00:04:06,979 --> 00:04:07,979
♪I can't control myself♪

73
00:04:08,620 --> 00:04:12,180
♪My mind is full of you♪

74
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:19,220
♪Stubborn and restless, every step is hard♪

75
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:22,379
♪I've always been cautious♪

76
00:04:22,740 --> 00:04:27,300
♪But now I want to tell you♪

77
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:30,699
♪I like you very much♪

78
00:04:30,939 --> 00:04:34,220
♪Like spring blossoms lasting into summer nights...♪

79
00:04:36,949 --> 00:04:37,949
It's been a while

80
00:04:37,949 --> 00:04:38,899
since you were this happy, right?

81
00:04:38,899 --> 00:04:41,779
♪Like tears falling into the sea, escaping loneliness♪

82
00:04:42,259 --> 00:04:45,579
♪I simply like you, without caring about the ending♪

83
00:04:47,740 --> 00:04:50,540
[Episode 12]
[How to Be Happy?]

84
00:04:57,420 --> 00:04:57,980
[3143 Days]

85
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,680
I'm living happily now.

86
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,360
I have my own family.

87
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,870
Please,

88
00:05:04,870 --> 00:05:06,430
stop looking for me.

89
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,310
Auntie,

90
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,949
if she doesn't want to see you,

91
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:12,750
please don't look for her.

92
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:23,480
Yuqing asked me

93
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:25,800
to give this to you.

94
00:05:41,870 --> 00:05:43,040
This is ransom money

95
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:46,160
to buy back her freedom?

96
00:05:46,949 --> 00:05:48,189
She hopes

97
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,629
you'll start a new life too.

98
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:51,360
Please, just let her go.

99
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,160
Goodbye.

100
00:06:31,189 --> 00:06:32,000
Yifan.

101
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:34,240
What's wrong?

102
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,629
Need my help with something?

103
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:37,040
No.

104
00:06:39,389 --> 00:06:39,870
Okay.

105
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:50,720
Yifan.

106
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,579
After you finish editing,

107
00:06:54,629 --> 00:06:56,240
will you come to my welcome party?

108
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,600
Not sure.

109
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:01,040
I'll see how things go.

110
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,389
But I really hope you will.

111
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:05,430
Yifan,

112
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:07,500
Still working? Everyone's left.

113
00:07:08,269 --> 00:07:09,199
Yeah, Yifan.

114
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,360
You have to come

115
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,240
to our welcome party!

116
00:07:11,269 --> 00:07:12,360
Please!

117
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:13,680
Come on.

118
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,069
Su Tian is already there.

119
00:07:15,069 --> 00:07:15,949
We're just waiting for you.

120
00:07:16,269 --> 00:07:16,870
Join us!

121
00:07:19,930 --> 00:07:21,420
Alright, I'll try once I'm done.

122
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:21,870
Okay?

123
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:23,160
Okay, we'll wait for you.

124
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,899
- Let's go! Mu Chengyun, hurry! - See you there.

125
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,600
So,

126
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,360
see you tonight.

127
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:48,480
Look at you.

128
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,800
Still thinking about sleep?

129
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,160
Alright.

130
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,069
Remember everything I said.

131
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,579
Yifan.

132
00:08:00,509 --> 00:08:01,269
Mr. Gan.

133
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:02,829
You're still here?

134
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,720
I just finished a meeting with them.

135
00:08:05,069 --> 00:08:06,360
Come on. Let's go join the party.

136
00:08:06,569 --> 00:08:07,509
I'm skipping.

137
00:08:07,509 --> 00:08:08,560
I'm heading home first.

138
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,269
Bye.

139
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,389
Yifan.

140
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,560
What's up?

141
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:19,870
This place

142
00:08:20,189 --> 00:08:22,189
isn't like Yihe Daily, right?

143
00:08:25,949 --> 00:08:27,149
If anyone

144
00:08:27,149 --> 00:08:28,759
harasses you in any way,

145
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:29,709
you have to tell me.

146
00:08:29,709 --> 00:08:30,910
I won't let them get away with it.

147
00:08:31,509 --> 00:08:32,080
No one has.

148
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:33,870
Good.

149
00:08:34,230 --> 00:08:35,110
I was just worried.

150
00:08:35,110 --> 00:08:36,679
You never join gatherings.

151
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:38,399
Is there another reason?

152
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:39,559
Really no.

153
00:08:41,110 --> 00:08:42,129
Our colleagues here

154
00:08:42,129 --> 00:08:43,679
are pretty easygoing, right?

155
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:46,399
Everyone's nice.

156
00:08:46,629 --> 00:08:48,110
So what's stopping you?

157
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:49,440
Alright, go grab your bag.

158
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,440
I'll go get the car.

159
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:51,799
Mr. Gan...

160
00:09:01,580 --> 00:09:04,340
[Overtime]

161
00:09:08,399 --> 00:09:09,990
Hello, we have a reservation.

162
00:09:11,570 --> 00:09:12,440
Miss Wen!

163
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,159
Your friends are upstairs.

164
00:09:14,350 --> 00:09:15,159
I'll take you to them.

165
00:09:17,470 --> 00:09:18,279
You've been here before?

166
00:09:19,629 --> 00:09:20,590
This way.

167
00:09:25,110 --> 00:09:26,350
Just head up, and you'll see them.

168
00:09:26,350 --> 00:09:27,080
Thanks.

169
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:35,679
Enjoying yourself?

170
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,200
Mr. Gan!

171
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,320
The boss is here!

172
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:38,990
Yifan.

173
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,870
Take a seat!

174
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,470
Yifan, sit here.

175
00:09:42,629 --> 00:09:43,679
- Thanks. - Let me get your bag.

176
00:09:43,679 --> 00:09:44,809
No need. I can handle it.

177
00:09:44,809 --> 00:09:45,470
It's fine. Leave it there.

178
00:09:45,470 --> 00:09:46,659
- So... - Thanks.

179
00:09:46,659 --> 00:09:47,919
Everyone,

180
00:09:48,629 --> 00:09:49,320
tonight,

181
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,590
we're here mainly

182
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:53,590
to welcome our two new colleagues.

183
00:09:54,230 --> 00:09:54,950
You two

184
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:56,919
don't need to be nervous.

185
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:58,679
Just treat this workplace like home.

186
00:09:58,990 --> 00:09:59,629
Also,

187
00:09:59,830 --> 00:10:01,559
everyone's been working hard.

188
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,110
Tonight,

189
00:10:03,830 --> 00:10:04,990
drink up

190
00:10:05,230 --> 00:10:06,279
and eat up!

191
00:10:06,399 --> 00:10:07,200
It's on me!

192
00:10:08,570 --> 00:10:10,250
That's what we've been waiting for!

193
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:11,350
Cheers!

194
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:12,470
Cheers, everyone!

195
00:10:12,470 --> 00:10:13,159
Cheers!

196
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:13,730
Come on!

197
00:10:13,730 --> 00:10:14,980
- Let's go! - Thanks.

198
00:10:52,350 --> 00:10:52,919
Boss.

199
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:54,279
Why bother coming over?

200
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,870
You worked all day already.

201
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:56,679
We got this.

202
00:10:56,679 --> 00:10:57,440
No need for you to worry.

203
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,230
Not welcome me?

204
00:10:58,470 --> 00:10:59,350
Boss, what do you want to drink?

205
00:10:59,350 --> 00:11:00,230
I'll mix one for you.

206
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:01,799
No drinking. I'm driving.

207
00:11:02,750 --> 00:11:03,399
By the way,

208
00:11:03,399 --> 00:11:04,750
your friends are holding a party upstairs.

209
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,350
Glad you came.

210
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:46,750
May I

211
00:11:47,230 --> 00:11:48,350
stand on your left?

212
00:11:51,679 --> 00:11:52,350
Why?

213
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,750
Because this way,

214
00:11:54,830 --> 00:11:56,110
I'll be closer to your heart.

215
00:12:04,629 --> 00:12:06,519
Just think of it as a reward

216
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:07,830
for my hard work these days.

217
00:12:11,350 --> 00:12:11,990
Yifan.

218
00:12:12,230 --> 00:12:13,080
Where's that classmate of yours?

219
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,080
We didn't see him today.

220
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,110
Who?

221
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,279
The one who's...

222
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:18,159
handsome and miserable.

223
00:12:18,470 --> 00:12:19,080
Who?

224
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:19,679
Here.

225
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:21,159
Check out my idol.

226
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:23,679
Look at him.

227
00:12:24,350 --> 00:12:25,950
Who stays this calm in a fire?

228
00:12:26,009 --> 00:12:27,720
[This side profile is amazing!]
Happy, I am very happy...

229
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:30,870
Isn't that Senior Sang Yan?

230
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,080
Senior?

231
00:12:32,629 --> 00:12:33,750
He's from our school, too?

232
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:34,519
Yeah.

233
00:12:35,110 --> 00:12:37,440
He was in the same class as another senior I'm close with.

234
00:12:37,470 --> 00:12:38,279
So, back then,

235
00:12:38,279 --> 00:12:39,440
I tagged along

236
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,200
to their graduation dinner.

237
00:12:40,399 --> 00:12:42,710
After the dinner,

238
00:12:42,830 --> 00:12:44,519
did anything crazy happen?

239
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:45,679
Not really.

240
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:47,559
But I do remember one thing.

241
00:12:47,919 --> 00:12:49,350
At the graduation dinner,

242
00:12:49,679 --> 00:12:51,039
most people

243
00:12:51,039 --> 00:12:52,159
had a few drinks,

244
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,080
except for two,

245
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,830
the legends of the Computer Science department,

246
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:57,629
Sang Yan and Duan Jiaxu.

247
00:12:58,230 --> 00:12:59,350
One didn't touch a drop,

248
00:12:59,590 --> 00:13:00,799
the other downed bottles like water,

249
00:13:00,799 --> 00:13:01,679
over ten bottles.

250
00:13:01,919 --> 00:13:02,950
Ten bottles?

251
00:13:03,350 --> 00:13:04,200
Who drank them?

252
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,159
Sang Yan.

253
00:13:27,279 --> 00:13:28,200
Are you okay?

254
00:13:31,679 --> 00:13:32,440
I'm fine.

255
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,470
I'm just a little unsteady.

256
00:13:37,870 --> 00:13:38,919
Unsteady, huh?

257
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:41,039
Let go.

258
00:13:43,799 --> 00:13:44,679
Let go.

259
00:13:46,110 --> 00:13:46,919
I'm talking to you.

260
00:13:54,399 --> 00:13:55,279
Senior Sang Yan.

261
00:13:55,629 --> 00:13:56,519
Who's your senior?

262
00:13:57,039 --> 00:13:58,710
I'm a Nanwu University student, too, you know.

263
00:13:58,870 --> 00:14:00,230
Could you be a little nicer to me?

264
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:02,710
Wen Yifan.

265
00:14:05,039 --> 00:14:05,590
Can you stand still?

266
00:14:07,230 --> 00:14:08,039
Then do me a favor.

267
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:08,750
Open the car door.

268
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:14,750
Need help?

269
00:14:15,279 --> 00:14:15,679
Yeah.

270
00:14:15,950 --> 00:14:16,519
No.

271
00:14:16,710 --> 00:14:17,750
You're clumsy

272
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:18,629
and careless.

273
00:14:18,629 --> 00:14:19,230
You can't take care

274
00:14:19,230 --> 00:14:20,470
of my frail junior!

275
00:14:20,470 --> 00:14:21,000
Yifan,

276
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:21,950
get in and sit next to me...

277
00:14:24,039 --> 00:14:24,950
I'm heading out.

278
00:14:27,110 --> 00:14:27,990
Take the front seat.

279
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:34,559
Hurry up.

280
00:14:38,990 --> 00:14:39,590
Mind our foot.

281
00:14:50,710 --> 00:14:51,279
Where do you live?

282
00:14:53,039 --> 00:14:53,919
Nanwu University.

283
00:15:04,990 --> 00:15:05,950
- We're here. - Wait in the car.

284
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,200
Thanks.

285
00:15:09,950 --> 00:15:10,830
Get up.

286
00:15:14,710 --> 00:15:15,590
Senior Sang Yan,

287
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:17,399
I can walk on my own.

288
00:15:17,559 --> 00:15:18,279
You're awake?

289
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,320
Aren't you an actor?

290
