00:38:49,110 --> 00:38:51,190
Are you dating...

581
00:38:51,519 --> 00:38:52,269
Sang Yan?

582
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:54,039
No.

583
00:38:55,559 --> 00:38:56,880
But he drove you to work

584
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:58,590
and even patted your head.

585
00:38:58,590 --> 00:38:59,710
So I thought...

586
00:39:01,309 --> 00:39:01,920
Alright, done.

587
00:39:04,190 --> 00:39:05,190
Did that count as patting?

588
00:39:05,710 --> 00:39:06,630
Miss Wen!

589
00:39:06,840 --> 00:39:08,360
Miss Wen, you have a package.

590
00:39:08,519 --> 00:39:09,110
Mine?

591
00:39:09,110 --> 00:39:09,519
Yes.

592
00:39:09,809 --> 00:39:10,710
I'll get it.

593
00:39:12,659 --> 00:39:13,880
- Thanks. - No problem.

594
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:15,000
Let's go.

595
00:39:15,150 --> 00:39:15,840
Is it heavy?

596
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:16,840
Not really.

597
00:39:17,400 --> 00:39:18,079
Thanks.

598
00:39:18,110 --> 00:39:18,789
No worries.

599
00:39:20,670 --> 00:39:21,449
Is it easy to carry?

600
00:39:21,519 --> 00:39:22,280
Piece of cake.

601
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,269
Morning, Fang Li.

602
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:26,679
- Morning! - Morning, Fang Li.

603
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:28,400
Morning.

604
00:39:30,789 --> 00:39:31,630
Just leave it here.

605
00:39:31,630 --> 00:39:32,150
Okay.

606
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:32,880
Thanks.

607
00:39:33,210 --> 00:39:33,760
Look.

608
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:35,630
What's up with those two?

609
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:36,590
I have no idea.

610
00:39:37,079 --> 00:39:38,750
They always come and go together.

611
00:39:38,880 --> 00:39:40,400
Are they dating?

612
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:42,150
What are they talking about?

613
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:44,670
Anyway, if you need help, I'm here.

614
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:46,039
Whatever you need.

615
00:39:48,150 --> 00:39:48,840
Thanks.

616
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:51,230
Want me to make you a coffee?

617
00:39:51,519 --> 00:39:52,440
No need, really.

618
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:55,000
It's fine. I wanted one anyway.

619
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:10,480
Dian,

620
00:40:10,710 --> 00:40:12,789
try using this next time you sleep.

621
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:15,190
It might stop the sleepwalking.

622
00:40:22,630 --> 00:40:23,360
Dian.

623
00:40:24,110 --> 00:40:25,269
I got the sleeping bag.

624
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,750
Isn't the package way too big?

625
00:40:27,150 --> 00:40:28,670
No need to thank me.

626
00:40:29,039 --> 00:40:30,559
I don't know if it'll work.

627
00:40:30,559 --> 00:40:31,519
But give it a shot.

628
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:32,480
Alright, bye.

629
00:40:32,630 --> 00:40:33,190
Okay.

630
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,269
Yifan!

631
00:40:46,630 --> 00:40:47,880
You're finally back!

632
00:40:48,150 --> 00:40:49,110
What are you doing here?

633
00:40:50,630 --> 00:40:51,230
So,

634
00:40:51,230 --> 00:40:52,190
Su Tian said

635
00:40:52,190 --> 00:40:53,750
your roommate moved out.

636
00:40:54,269 --> 00:40:54,750
I want

637
00:40:54,750 --> 00:40:56,480
to move out of the dorms.

638
00:40:56,789 --> 00:40:58,039
So I was hoping to check out

639
00:40:58,190 --> 00:40:59,309
the place you're renting.

640
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:02,000
That might not be a good idea.

641
00:41:05,440 --> 00:41:06,559
But I'm already here.

642
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:08,519
I know it's sudden,

643
00:41:08,519 --> 00:41:09,440
but I promise

644
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:10,400
I won't take up much of your time.

645
00:41:11,079 --> 00:41:11,670
But...

646
00:41:27,309 --> 00:41:28,559
Coming home late without a word?

647
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:35,920
Why did you get off work so early today?

648
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:40,840
Sorry for the intrusion, Senior Sang.

649
00:41:50,619 --> 00:41:56,460
[Episode 12]
[How to Be Happy? Staying with You]

650
00:42:07,219 --> 00:42:08,739
[Nanwu TV Station]

651
00:42:08,789 --> 00:42:09,400
Thanks.

652
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:15,230
[The story is not over yet...]

653
00:42:15,230 --> 00:42:15,880
Wen Yifan.

654
00:42:18,039 --> 00:42:19,750
You've... got something on your head.

655
00:42:19,960 --> 00:42:20,630
You can't see it.

656
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:22,559
Come closer.

657
00:42:24,750 --> 00:42:25,519
Come closer.

658
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:40,849
Alright, done.

659
00:42:41,809 --> 00:42:42,840
Stay safe.

660
00:42:46,710 --> 00:42:47,559
Morning, Yifan.

661
00:42:47,670 --> 00:42:48,269
Morning.

662
00:43:08,659 --> 00:43:09,980
♪Even the strongest heart♪

663
00:43:10,139 --> 00:43:11,860
♪Can waver♪

664
00:43:12,139 --> 00:43:15,260
♪And doubt its fire♪

665
00:43:15,579 --> 00:43:17,219
♪But you never lost faith in me♪

666
00:43:17,219 --> 00:43:18,860
♪In every battle, every dream I chased♪

667
00:43:19,019 --> 00:43:21,739
♪There is meaning in every step I made♪

668
00:43:22,539 --> 00:43:28,500
♪Through the storm, through the endless night♪

669
00:43:28,900 --> 00:43:30,539
♪You were there, shining like a light♪

670
00:43:30,539 --> 00:43:32,219
♪Warm and bright♪

671
00:43:32,380 --> 00:43:36,099
♪Standing right by my side♪

672
00:43:36,539 --> 00:43:42,659
♪It was you, striding toward me through the storm♪

673
00:43:43,019 --> 00:43:49,940
♪It was you, always cheering me on♪

674
00:43:50,099 --> 00:43:53,099
♪The road is rough♪

675
00:43:53,420 --> 00:43:57,539
♪The rain won't stop♪

676
00:43:57,739 --> 00:44:01,699
♪But with you here♪

677
00:44:01,980 --> 00:44:08,019
♪I fear no dark♪

678
00:44:11,260 --> 00:44:14,860
♪Every thought, every memory is filled with you♪

679
00:44:15,179 --> 00:44:18,659
♪Marking our youth with every step we took♪

680
00:44:18,940 --> 00:44:20,820
♪When the downpour falls from the sky♪

681
00:44:20,820 --> 00:44:24,460
♪You're the one holding out an umbrella for me♪

682
00:44:24,820 --> 00:44:28,380
♪When the white dove brings the news♪

683
00:44:28,739 --> 00:44:32,179
♪You're the first I want to tell♪

684
00:44:32,579 --> 00:44:41,219
♪I won't give up. I'll stay right here with you♪

685
00:44:45,820 --> 00:44:52,019
♪It was you, striding toward me through the storm♪

686
00:44:52,860 --> 00:44:59,300
♪It was you, always cheering me on♪

687
00:44:59,300 --> 00:45:02,460
♪The road is rough♪

688
00:45:02,940 --> 00:45:06,900
♪The rain won't stop♪

689
00:45:07,099 --> 00:45:09,739
♪But with you here♪

690
00:45:09,940 --> 00:45:13,780
♪I will never give up♪

691
00:45:14,059 --> 00:45:20,139
♪You are my courage, my hope for the sky beyond♪

692
00:45:20,659 --> 00:45:26,500
♪You are my light, shining through every night♪

693
00:45:27,059 --> 00:45:29,900
♪Even if I have to walk alone someday♪

694
00:45:30,340 --> 00:45:33,179
♪I'll never truly be on my own♪

695
00:45:34,219 --> 00:45:38,739
♪'Cause knowing you're here♪

696
00:45:39,179 --> 00:45:45,780
♪I can brave the dark ahead♪

697
00:45:47,579 --> 00:45:48,840
[Huge thanks to everyone involved and to all the fans of The First Frost!]

698
00:45:48,840 --> 00:45:49,980
[Treat yourself well, and the world will hold more love for you!]
